  <thing id="wWhipPrikl" name="Prickle Whip" description="A prickle whip is a strand from a bramble creauture. A prickle whip deals lethal damage and is not negated by armor or natural armor of any value. The whip is treated as a melee weapon with 15-foot reach, though you don&apos;t threaten the area into which you can make an attack. In addition, unlike most other weapons with reach, you can use it against foes anywhere within your reach (including adjacent foes).\n\nUsing a whip provokes an attack of opportunity, just as if you had used a ranged weapon.\n\nYou can use the Weapon Finesse feat to apply your Dexterity modifier instead of your Strength modifier to attack rolls with a whip sized for you, even though it isn&apos;t a light weapon." compset="Weapon">
